headline: EU seeks fresh delay to deforestation rules amid IT headaches
summary: The Commission is blaming IT problems for the prospect of a fresh delay to the rules, known as EUDR.

headline: NY Cocoa Prices Climb as Supplies Tighten
summary: December ICE NY cocoa (CCZ25 ) on Tuesday closed up +33 (+0.47%), and December ICE London cocoa #7 (CAZ25 ) closed down -22 (-0.45%).
